{
  "id": "hoa-hook",
  "title": "HOA ornaments demo",
  "fixture": "hoa-ornaments-funny-demo",
  "start_seconds": 0,
  "duration_seconds": 103.635,
  "entries": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Alright, next up is the neighborhood HOA ornament complaint. I'm Laura, chairing tonight, Will filed it, and Maya owns several of the flamingos in question.",
      "start_seconds": 0.18,
      "end_seconds": 10.368
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "My complaint is simple, the front yards are becoming a themed miniature golf course.",
      "start_seconds": 10.526,
      "end_seconds": 16.116
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "That is extremely generous, thank you.",
      "start_seconds": 16.274,
      "end_seconds": 18.625
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "I prepared a brief, with exhibits.",
      "start_seconds": 18.783,
      "end_seconds": 21.082
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "He brought exhibits, for gnomes.",
      "start_seconds": 21.24,
      "end_seconds": 23.669
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "Forty-two pages, mostly photos.",
      "start_seconds": 23.827,
      "end_seconds": 26.178
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "We're not reading forty-two pages.",
      "start_seconds": 26.336,
      "end_seconds": 28.374
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "On Maple Court alone, I counted nineteen flamingos.",
      "start_seconds": 28.532,
      "end_seconds": 31.876
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Nine of those are mine, and they have names.",
      "start_seconds": 32.034,
      "end_seconds": 35.352
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "That's the problem, Maya, they have names.",
      "start_seconds": 35.51,
      "end_seconds": 38.096
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Phyllis is a delight.",
      "start_seconds": 38.254,
      "end_seconds": 40.292
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "Phyllis is a code violation.",
      "start_seconds": 40.45,
      "end_seconds": 41.405,
      "is_interrupted": true
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Sorry, can I just-",
      "start_seconds": 41.145,
      "end_seconds": 42.242,
      "overlaps_with": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "Sure, go ahead.",
      "start_seconds": 42.342,
      "end_seconds": 43.57
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "The bylaws say tasteful, that's the whole sentence.",
      "start_seconds": 43.728,
      "end_seconds": 46.915
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Right.",
      "start_seconds": 47.073,
      "end_seconds": 47.648
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "And tasteful clearly excludes a plastic bird in a top hat.",
      "start_seconds": 47.806,
      "end_seconds": 51.881
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Phyllis wears a sunhat, it's seasonal.",
      "start_seconds": 52.039,
      "end_seconds": 54.338
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "She wore a Santa hat in July.",
      "start_seconds": 54.496,
      "end_seconds": 56.612
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Christmas in July is a thing, Will.",
      "start_seconds": 56.77,
      "end_seconds": 58.886
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "It is not a thing recognized by the bylaws, and frankly, this sets a dangerous-",
      "start_seconds": 59.044,
      "end_seconds": 62.942,
      "is_interrupted": true
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Will, it's a flamingo in a hat.",
      "start_seconds": 62.522,
      "end_seconds": 64.377,
      "overlaps_with": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "To clarify, I just mean once we allow one hat, we've opened the door to costumes.",
      "start_seconds": 64.417,
      "end_seconds": 69.929
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Still no.",
      "start_seconds": 70.087,
      "end_seconds": 70.897
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Can I say something, because actually-",
      "start_seconds": 71.055,
      "end_seconds": 73.275
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "If I could just-",
      "start_seconds": 71.575,
      "end_seconds": 72.777,
      "overlaps_with": 24
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Maya has the floor, Will.",
      "start_seconds": 72.857,
      "end_seconds": 74.268
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "Thank you, last summer, three kids knocked on my door just to meet Phyllis.",
      "start_seconds": 74.426,
      "end_seconds": 81.087
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "Maya, that's technically trespassing.",
      "start_seconds": 81.245,
      "end_seconds": 82.92,
      "is_interrupted": true
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "That's community.",
      "start_seconds": 82.74,
      "end_seconds": 83.863,
      "overlaps_with": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "And we still haven't addressed the pirate ship.",
      "start_seconds": 84.023,
      "end_seconds": 86.27
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "The pirate ship is tabled until I have emotional support.",
      "start_seconds": 86.428,
      "end_seconds": 89.38
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "Can we vote please, before I age another year.",
      "start_seconds": 89.501,
      "end_seconds": 92.27
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "speaker_id": "will",
      "speaker_name": "Will",
      "text": "I move to ban all decorative wildlife and humanoid figures under three feet.",
      "start_seconds": 92.428,
      "end_seconds": 97.313
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "speaker_id": "maya",
      "speaker_name": "Maya",
      "text": "I move to make Phyllis the official mascot.",
      "start_seconds": 97.471,
      "end_seconds": 100.135
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "speaker_id": "laura",
      "speaker_name": "Laura",
      "text": "I move that we adjourn and I go scream into a pillow.",
      "start_seconds": 100.293,
      "end_seconds": 103.375
    }
  ]
}
